object.script:
function onTick() iX = input.getNumber(3) iY = input.getNumber(4) ips = input.getBool(1) mode = input.getBool(2) modet = ips and ipr(iX, iY, 1, 23, 30, 8) n1 = input.getNumber(11) n2 = input.getNumber(12) n3 = input.getNumber(13) n4 = input.getNumber(14) n5 = input.getNumber(15) n6 = input.getNumber(16)
output.setBool(1, modet) selectt(1,9,11) selectt(6,9,13) selectt(11,9,15) selectt(16,9,17) selectt(21,9,19) selectt(26,9,21) end
function ipr(x, y, rectX, rectY, rectW, rectH) return x > rectX and y > rectY and x < rectX+rectW and y < rectY+rectH end
function select(x,y,z) screen.setColor(50, 50, 50) screen.drawLine(x+1, y, x+1, y-2) screen.drawLine(x+2, y, x+2, y-3) screen.drawLine(x+3, y, x+3, y-2) screen.drawLine(x+1, y+8, x+1, y+9.5) screen.drawLine(x+2, y+8, x+2, y+10.5) screen.drawLine(x+3, y+8, x+3, y+9.5) screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawText(x+1,y+2,string.format("%0.0f", z)) end function selectt(x,y,z) tu = ips and ipr(iX, iY, x, y-4, 5, 5) td = ips and ipr(iX, iY, x, y+7, 5, 5) output.setBool(z, tu) output.setBool(z+1, td) end
function onDraw() screen.setColor(3, 3, 3) screen.drawRectF(0, 0, 32, 32) select(1,9,n1) select(6,9,n2) select(11,9,n3) select(16,9,n4) select(21,9,n5) select(26,9,n6) screen.setColor(100, 100, 100) screen.drawText(2,1,"ci") screen.drawText(11,1,"pher") screen.drawRect(1, 23, 30, 8) if mode==true then screen.drawTextBox(1, 24, 30, 7, "safe", 0, 0) else screen.drawTextBox(1, 24, 30, 7, "plain", 0, 0) screen.setColor(50, 0, 0) screen.drawLine(1, 1, 31, 21) screen.drawLine(1, 21, 31, 1) end end
